ygData.messageBody:
At level 4 in qeynos i suggest staying in north qeynos for another level and
then going down to west karana and hunt the young lions, young lionesses,
wolfs, and brown bears until a bit higher which is when you should be able
to attack giant beetles and then giant spiders and then grizzly bears.
